{"tid":1442720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有關一陣北角既事 請入 聽君一言","createTime":"2019-08-11T04:46:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T04:52:33.000Z","uid":38165,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"405e619ddff985e1490a2edce0508573a8fc950d","tid":1442720,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:46:02.000Z","msg":"首先我唔係五毛 可起底 <br />\n所有中計撚 散水撚 分化撚全撚部死返出去 屌你地老母<br />\n我而個post唔係叫人唔好去或者叫人去<br />\n我知無論 和理非又好 勇武又好 大家情同手足<br />\n大家都好有腦 唔係都唔能夠同而個極權政府鬥咁耐<br />\n但係黑警今日唯獨批左維園集會已經好有問題<br />\n班狗當然想我地開波 跟住就懶係野咁樣捉晒兩邊人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>再放撚晒班黑社會</strong></span><br />\n我相信所有手足既智慧<br />\n<br />\n係到想多謝每一位為香港付出既香港人 手足<br />\n無你地我地生存唔到咁耐 <br />\n多謝你地<br />\n我今是日與你地同行<br />\n<br />\n我想各位可以應承我一件事<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不受傷 不被捕 <br />\n好唔好？我已經受唔住再有一位手足有事...</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後一句<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">煲撚大721元朗恐襲</span></span>"},{"pid":"a1d0f2f3d4eadefa429753f126d052cbce527954","tid":1442720,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:46:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721 721 721 721</span>"},{"pid":"a99c8bef200db4c682fc8020771b2cceed411ad1","tid":1442720,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:46:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721 721 721 元朗</span></span>"},{"pid":"c7e7c6c7e3485e2e1cf8d4c11ff2b716ccbec41b","tid":1442720,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:47:06.000Z","msg":"請用721 推post"},{"pid":"0e368f0547cf5e1e6c94b0f543fceb1099b3cbc4","tid":1442720,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:47:16.000Z","msg":"721 721 721 721"},{"pid":"ee01cb55adcae866a20991f5511b1cf1afeedb29","tid":1442720,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T0